== 诊断 ==
扭伤通常可以根据患者的体征和症状、损伤机制和[[体格检查|体格检查]]进行临床诊断。但是，[[X射线|X射线]]可以帮助识别骨折，特别是在受伤部位有{{le|压痛|Tenderness (medicine)}}或骨痛的情况下。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Vuurberg|first=Gwendolyn|last2=Hoorntje|first2=Alexander|last3=Wink|first3=Lauren M.|last4=Doelen|first4=Brent F. W. van der|last5=Bekerom|first5=Michel P. van den|last6=Dekker|first6=Rienk|last7=Dijk|first7=C. Niek van|last8=Krips|first8=Rover|last9=Loogman|first9=Masja C. M.|last10=Ridderikhof|first10=Milan L.|last11=Smithuis|first11=Frank F.|date=2018-08-01|title=Diagnosis, treatment and prevention of ankle sprains: update of an evidence-based clinical guideline|url=https://bjsm.bmj.com/content/52/15/956|journal=British Journal of Sports Medicine|language=en|volume=52|issue=15|pages=956|doi=10.1136/bjsports-2017-098106|issn=0306-3674|pmid=29514819|doi-access=free|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119032718/https://bjsm.bmj.com/content/52/15/956|dead-url=no}}</ref>在某些情况下，特别是如果愈合过程延长或怀疑有更严重的损伤，则进行[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]（MRI）以检查周围的[[软组织|软组织]]和[[韧带|韧带]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mayoclinic.com/health/sprains-and-strains/DS00343/|title=Sprains - Symptoms and causes|publisher=[[梅奥诊所医学中心|梅奥诊所医学中心]]|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2019-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731140734/http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/sprains-and-strains/DS00343|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 分类 ===
#一级扭伤（轻度） – 韧带轻微{{le|拉伸|Stretching}}和结构性损伤，导致轻度肿胀和瘀伤。患者通常没有关节不稳或关节活动范围减小。
#二度扭伤（中度） – 受影响的韧带部分撕裂。患者通常会出现中度肿胀、压痛和关节不稳。受影响的关节可能难以承重。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.health.harvard.edu/a_to_z/sprain-overview-a-to-z|title=Sprain (Overview)|last=Publishing|first=Harvard Health|website=Harvard Health|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119032121/https://www.health.harvard.edu/a_to_z/sprain-overview-a-to-z|dead-url=no}}</ref>
#三度扭伤（严重） – 韧带完全断裂或撕裂，有时{{le|撕脱性骨折|Avulsion fracture|撕脱一块骨头}}。患者通常会出现严重的关节不稳、疼痛、瘀伤、肿胀和无法对关节施加重量。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.orthoinfo.org/en/diseases--conditions/sprains-strains-and-other-soft-tissue-injuries/|title=Sprains, Strains and Other Soft-Tissue Injuries - OrthoInfo - AAOS|website=www.orthoinfo.org|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2020-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608111057/https://www.orthoinfo.org/en/diseases--conditions/sprains-strains-and-other-soft-tissue-injuries/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

