=== 涉及的关节 ===
尽管任何关节都可能发生扭伤，但一些更常见的损伤包括：<ref name=":5" />

*[[踝关节|踝关节]] - 扭伤最常见于踝关节，愈合时间比踝关节骨折要长。大多数踝关节扭伤通常发生在踝关节外侧的外侧韧带。常见的原因包括在不平坦的路面或在接触性运动中行走。<ref>{{cite book | first1 = David | last1 = Shier | first2 = Jackie | last2 = Butler | first3 = Ricki | last3 = Lewis | name-list-format = vanc |title=Hole's Human Anatomy & Physiology | url = https://archive.org/details/holeshumananatom0000shie_t3b6 |date=2007 |publisher=McGraw Hill / Irwin |isbn=978-0-07-330555-4 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/holeshumananatom0000shie_t3b6/page/157 157], 160 |edition=11th}}</ref> 
**内翻性踝关节扭伤 - 踝关节内翻时发生的损伤
**外翻性踝关节扭伤 - 踝关节外翻时发生的损伤
*[[脚趾|脚趾]]
**{{le|跖趾关节扭伤|Metatarsophalangeal joint sprain}} - 迫使大脚趾向上过度伸展，尤其在运动中（在硬的地面上开始冲刺）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.orthoinfo.org/en/diseases--conditions/turf-toe/|title=Turf Toe - OrthoInfo - AAOS|website=www.orthoinfo.org|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208014620/https://www.orthoinfo.org/en/diseases--conditions/turf-toe/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*[[膝关节|膝关节]] - 扭伤通常发生在膝关节，尤其发生在{{le|接触性运动|Contact sport}}（[[美式足球|美式足球]]、[[足球|足球]]、[[篮球|篮球]]、[[撑竿跳高|撑竿跳高]]、[[垒球|垒球]]、[[棒球|棒球]]和某些类型的[[武术|武术]]）中。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.health.harvard.edu/a_to_z/knee-sprain-a-to-z|title=Knee Sprain|last=Publishing|first=Harvard Health|website=Harvard Health|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121224849/https://www.health.harvard.edu/a_to_z/knee-sprain-a-to-z|dead-url=no}}</ref>
**{{le|前交叉韧带损伤|Anterior cruciate ligament injury|前交叉韧带（ACL）损伤}}
**{{le|后交叉韧带损伤|Posterior cruciate ligament injury|后交叉韧带（PCL）损伤}}
**内侧副韧带（MCL）损伤
**外侧副韧带（LCL）损伤
**上胫腓关节扭伤 - 通常由连接[[胫骨|胫骨]]和[[腓骨|腓骨]]的关节扭伤引起
**{{le|髌骨脱位|Patellar dislocation}}
*[[手指|手指]]和[[手腕|手腕]] - 手腕扭伤经常发生，尤其是在摔倒时伸出的手上。
**{{le|拇指尺侧副韧带损伤|Ulnar collateral ligament injury of the thumb}}（{{lang|en|Ulnar collateral ligament injury of the thumb}}）（又称滑雪者拇指，猎人拇指）用力抓握导致拇指掌指关节（MCP）的尺侧副韧带（UCL）受伤，历史上在苏格兰猎场看守人中被发现<ref>{{Cite book|last=Hung|first=Chen-Yu|title=Gamekeepers Thumb (Skiers, Ulnar Collateral Ligament Tear)|date=2020|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK499971/|work=StatPearls|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|pmid=29763146|access-date=2020-07-13|last2=Varacallo|first2=Matthew|last3=Chang|first3=Ke-Vin}}</ref>
*[[脊柱|脊柱]]
**[[颈椎|颈椎]]颈部扭伤
**外伤性颈椎综合征（{{lang|en|Traumatic Cervical Spine Syndrome}}) - 颈部被迫过度伸展和弯曲，常见于[[追尾|追尾]]车祸中<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Tanaka|first=Nobuhiro|last2=Atesok|first2=Kivanc|last3=Nakanishi|first3=Kazuyoshi|last4=Kamei|first4=Naosuke|last5=Nakamae|first5=Toshio|last6=Kotaka|first6=Shinji|last7=Adachi|first7=Nobuo|date=2018-02-28|title=Pathology and Treatment of Traumatic Cervical Spine Syndrome: Whiplash Injury|journal=Advances in Orthopedics|volume=2018|pages=4765050|doi=10.1155/2018/4765050|issn=2090-3464|pmc=5851023|pmid=29682354}}</ref>
